{"tid":2054870,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人pc用Netgear Orbi rbk20會斷網?","createTime":"2020-06-07T13:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T16:59:32.000Z","uid":71619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fca82299614939b6655ef2618d24c2a490bac731","tid":2054870,"uid":71619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"我個set up係modem去Router再去orbi主機(用AP mode)無線連去衛星入我房再用lan線連我部電腦<br />\r\n開頭一個月無乜問題，幾滿意，依加真係話斷就斷 唔好彩既1分鐘斷2次 好彩既半日唔斷(我用依個網睇<a href=\"https://ping.canbeuseful.com/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fping.canbeuseful.com%2Fen&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUpMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=1d640167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ping.canbeuseful.com/en</a>)<br />\r\n起初以為orbi都係垃圾但我發現原來只有我部電腦斷，我做過個測試(電腦斷嗰陣, ipad,電話,ps4都無斷)<br />\r\n後來我電腦唔插lan轉用wifi，一樣照會斷，完全打唔到機，每次玩緊嗰陣都會祈禱唔好斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r\n試過好多方法，又試過update orbi主機同個衛星，又試過重裝過部電腦都係唔得<br />\r\n但係我觀察到個現象，我唔斷線嗰日個上網速度係大約10MB/s，會斷嗰陣係40-50MB/s<br />\r\n有無人可以打救我，我都係想上網打機啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有乜理由淨係電腦斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有唔明我可以補充"},{"pid":"8c794fafa098de77359110ee6a87e8e387d5f1a3","tid":2054870,"uid":140879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"樓主咁慘大家幫下佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff024407428e659e34d2c9057048e9c335f2b58","tid":2054870,"uid":230043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:41:45.000Z","msg":"鳩up 下先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試下斷晒其他devices 淨係比電腦上網<br />\n<br />\n可能隻野overload  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2ef3c4966e1350a276e6b9a20d33f4d3864704","tid":2054870,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"首先試下唔用satellite 會點<br />\n試下reset satellite<br />\n試下用返router mode"},{"pid":"970ddf618fc0eb3b557fb854625e7d184f046b48","tid":2054870,"uid":149051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"仲靠網絡供應商？<br />\n自己去鴨記買幾塊電子板<br />\n五金鋪買料整支丫叉<br />\n射上天<br />\nRefresh一次部機就得"}]}